WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:14.812
Hi, my name is Brandon. I've had—I won't call it a visitation, but I saw some things when I was praying in the spirit, and I want to tell you what the Lord showed me.

00:00:14.812 --> 00:00:20.504
All right, here we go. I was praying just like I do on a normal night.

00:00:20.505 --> 00:00:24.484
It wasn't anything special; there wasn't anything different about the prayer.

00:00:24.485 --> 00:00:31.288
I was just interceding, and it was in a Chinese-like dialect.

00:00:31.289 --> 00:00:37.163
It was different, but it was deep intercession, so I figured I was praying for somebody.

00:00:37.164 --> 00:00:52.984
In my spirit eyes, what the Lord opens up to me whenever I'm interceding for somebody, or the country, or whatever—a lot of times he'll give me cues and show me the direction I'm going or who I'm praying for.

00:00:52.985 --> 00:01:08.102
In this, I started to go into deep groanings. It was very intense, different than any other time I've had in a long time.

00:01:08.103 --> 00:01:13.792
Out of my innermost being, out of my spirit, it was coming up and rolling out of me.

00:01:13.793 --> 00:01:20.458
In my intercession, I couldn't get tongues out fast enough for what I was interceding for.

00:01:20.459 --> 00:01:27.359
It's like I birthed it, and I was translated in my spirit eyes.

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:35.999
I was in this jungle-like place, and that’s all I could see on both sides of me, but I was being ushered in.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:44.626
It was like I was being pushed from behind very quickly, and all of a sudden, I saw this temple in front of me.

00:01:44.627 --> 00:02:05.127
I went into this temple that was like beautiful platinum, but it wasn't gold or silver; it was see-through, almost transparent, the most beautiful metal.

00:02:05.128 --> 00:02:10.300
I don't know what the throne room was; I've never seen that on this Earth before.

00:02:10.301 --> 00:02:23.206
I went into this temple and saw this being on a throne. It was carved out and beautiful.

00:02:23.207 --> 00:02:35.234
I could see the throne, but I could only see a glimpse. I looked up because, as I walked in, he was high and lifted up.

00:02:35.235 --> 00:02:55.395
I glimpsed and thought in my spirit, 'Where am I? Who is this?'And he said, 'I Am that I Am.'When he said that, he shook the whole temple.

00:02:55.396 --> 00:03:05.062
The foundation, everything was being shaken by his words. I screamed; it freaked me out because it was so powerful.

00:03:05.063 --> 00:03:18.119
At that time, I glanced up to the top and could see this gold and this red ruby.

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:32.438
It was gorgeous. All of a sudden, a light beyond any kind of light I've ever seen appeared.

00:03:32.439 --> 00:03:43.639
There's nothing on this Earth as bright as what I saw. You can look at the sun at noon, and it's still not as bright.

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:52.552
There were three stages of light: a light that wasn't as bright, a brighter light, and then the center light.

00:03:52.553 --> 00:03:57.978
The light in the center was so bright it was piercing; if you looked at it, it would melt you.

00:03:57.979 --> 00:04:05.420
I couldn't look at it. I could see the outer light, but I tried to glance up and it was piercing me.

00:04:05.421 --> 00:04:14.730
It was incredible; words cannot describe what I'm trying to say.

00:04:14.731 --> 00:04:24.476
The English vocabulary does not wrap around my intellect to tell you what I was seeing.

00:04:24.477 --> 00:04:38.403
Let me say it like living water. When he spoke, his words would go out and stay alive.

00:04:38.404 --> 00:04:48.430
I can't skip around too far. Whenever I was at the altar, there was water at the base of it.

00:04:48.431 --> 00:05:06.460
It was ankle-deep, knee-deep, and waist-deep, and then you could see in the deep it went over an edge and went way down.

00:05:06.461 --> 00:05:12.997
In this water, you could take your whole body all the way to the bottom.

00:05:12.998 --> 00:05:19.193
The water was the clearest, bluest, most beautiful water I've ever seen.

00:05:19.194 --> 00:05:24.676
You could just drink it and want more because the water was so perfect.

00:05:24.677 --> 00:05:40.790
It was flowing out of the throne, flowing out of him; it was living water.

00:05:40.791 --> 00:05:58.886
He spoke to me for about an hour in this encounter about the end times, the church, and personal stuff about my life and family.

00:05:58.887 --> 00:06:18.792
When he spoke, his words would come out of that light in English, but they would be really big, then stop upon the water and get smaller until they turned into a seed.

00:06:18.793 --> 00:06:24.168
The words wouldn't die; they remained alive and would start to grow. They were like a seed right in front of your face.

00:06:24.169 --> 00:06:25.789
They started growing and cultivating roots, like a potato or a peanut in a farm.

00:06:25.790 --> 00:07:12.702
The words became alive. Every time he would speak, they would start to form and grow together.

00:07:12.703 --> 00:07:33.662
I know the Bible says we are made in his image, but he is God. All of a sudden, out of that light, a massive eyeball came out.

00:07:33.663 --> 00:07:44.063
It was an all-seeing eye. It came right up within probably fifteen feet of me.

00:07:44.064 --> 00:07:55.774
It was everything I could do not to wet myself; that’s how intense and scary it was.

00:07:55.775 --> 00:08:01.040
All I wanted to do was cry out in repentance and ask God to forgive me.

00:08:01.041 --> 00:08:20.947
He is holy and merciful. It shook me to the core. In that eye, in the iris, there was fire.

00:08:20.948 --> 00:08:36.592
The fire was growing and moving; it was alive. The flames were dancing upon each other.

00:08:36.593 --> 00:08:59.897
It was so intense. Every time he spoke, the words came out of that light. He talked to me about a verse I had been discussing with him.

00:08:59.898 --> 00:09:13.822
I’ve been hearing from certain ministers that there is no end-time revival, but I was asking him about this.

00:09:13.823 --> 00:09:26.849
I quoted the scripture, 'As the days of Noah, so will it be when the Son of Man returns.'They were put in the boat and left; there was no big revival.

00:09:26.850 --> 00:09:32.842
I was praying in tongues, and he was speaking to me in tongues.

00:09:32.843 --> 00:09:59.440
His tongue was very deep and masculine, like echoes, like living water flowing out of him. It was a heavenly language I’ve never heard before.

00:09:59.441 --> 00:10:19.190
His tongue was like roaring thunder when he spoke, but I understood everything he was saying. When I spoke in tongues, he understood me.

00:10:19.191 --> 00:10:27.755
We were talking to each other, and I understood him in English in my ears even though it was in tongues.

00:10:27.756 --> 00:10:46.212
He was speaking to me as 'I Am that I Am.'I hope my words are giving some justice to this.

00:10:46.213 --> 00:10:53.594
He said, 'Son, you have no idea the real translation of those scriptures.

00:10:53.595 --> 00:11:02.326
You need to go back to the Greek and study my word more than just the King James or the Amplified versions.

00:11:02.327 --> 00:11:12.328
Study the meaning of each word.'He asked, 'Who says that I'm coming back right now?'I mentioned the signs of the times.

00:11:12.329 --> 00:11:35.008
He said, 'I am in control of time,'and he shook the foundation of the temple. 'I will come back when I am ready.

00:11:35.009 --> 00:11:43.778
I said in my word that I'm coming back for a spotless bride, and the bride is not ready yet.

00:11:43.779 --> 00:11:47.755
My Son's return—he doesn't even know, nor the angels in heaven.

00:11:47.756 --> 00:12:07.048
I will come back when I am ready.'I was quoting scriptures back to him with my little peanut brain, but he was quoting back a thousand more.

00:12:07.049 --> 00:12:21.965
It was just flowing out of him. He said, 'I want to show you something.'I hope I’m not skipping around, but the Spirit will bring stuff back to me.

00:12:21.966 --> 00:12:36.434
There was a preacher—I will not release his name—who was interceding on the Earth. The Lord allowed me to hear his prayer.

00:12:36.435 --> 00:12:47.210
I was standing at the altar, and I saw a shaft of light like a flaming comet coming up from the Earth.

00:12:47.211 --> 00:12:57.867
It circled the throne room; they were prayers echoing from this man.

00:12:57.868 --> 00:13:10.664
He was interceding for the continents of the world, and they were coming up before the Father.

00:13:10.665 --> 00:13:24.599
This man came to the throne room in the spirit, and a transparent globe wrapped around him.

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:44.358
Beams of light were coming out of his belly, shooting to places on the globe like South America, Europe, Asia, America, and Canada.

00:13:44.359 --> 00:14:09.100
He was interceding for an end-time revival. The Lord told me, 'Go and tell this family member that their theology of no end-time revival is nonsense.

00:14:09.101 --> 00:14:22.160
There will be a great revival, a harvest of souls, an outpouring of my Spirit, and many healings.

00:14:22.161 --> 00:14:37.293
I will not be defeated, and you will not be defeated. You will walk in a great victory in these last days. I am not coming back for a church that is weak and defeated.

00:14:37.294 --> 00:14:58.314
You will go forth into this world and do what I've called you to do with great victory.'He said many people have an escape mentality.

00:14:58.315 --> 00:15:08.608
'You will not have an escape mentality because times are hard. You will press into me and walk in my glory.

00:15:08.609 --> 00:15:37.807
I never designed the armor for retreat; I designed it for charging ahead and taking dominion.'He said the teaching that there is no end-time revival is nonsense.

00:15:37.808 --> 00:15:44.665
When he said that, he was angry, and it shook the foundation.

00:15:44.666 --> 00:16:06.297
He said there are challenging times ahead. There's a great shifting—like corn being shucked.

00:16:06.298 --> 00:16:12.425
He said, 'I'm going to shuck the corn, son.'I'm from Oklahoma, so I get that.

00:16:12.426 --> 00:16:32.132
'We're going to pull it back, clean it up, and make it ready.'He showed me the bride in the throne room.

00:16:32.133 --> 00:16:56.405
She had a beautiful lace gown, but it had black spots and smudges like soot.

00:16:56.406 --> 00:17:02.520
He said, 'I told you in my word that I'm coming back for a spotless bride.

00:17:02.521 --> 00:17:33.174
It's time for you to come out of the ankle-deep water and come to the deeper water.'I wanted to go in that deep water so bad.

00:17:33.175 --> 00:17:40.463
He said, 'Brandon, you've been in that deeper water before. It's like muscle memory.

00:17:40.464 --> 00:17:54.935
You'll build your muscles up spiritually and just flow back into it.

00:17:54.936 --> 00:18:26.430
Seek me.'He talked to me about finances because I’ve been praying for million-dollar ideas.

00:18:26.431 --> 00:18:36.119
He said sternly, 'Where in my word did I tell you to pray like that?

00:18:36.120 --> 00:18:44.527
Seek first the kingdom, and all these things will be added unto you.

00:18:44.528 --> 00:19:00.435
Seeking finances that way is idolatry. Seek me, and I will give you the secret things.

00:19:00.436 --> 00:19:10.059
I have no problem blessing you with money as long as that money doesn't have you.

00:19:10.060 --> 00:19:44.645
As soon as I can trust you with that outflow, you'll have it.'I told him I was sorry and that I wanted to be spotless and usable.

00:19:44.646 --> 00:19:54.294
Jesus is coming back for a victorious church, not one that is retreating.

00:19:54.295 --> 00:20:21.425
The gospel that must be preached is repentance. We must seek his face and know his heart.

00:20:21.426 --> 00:21:17.941
He said, 'If you lay your head upon my chest every day, I will whisper the secret things to you in a still, small voice.'I was interceding for America and crying out for revival on the East Coast.

00:21:17.942 --> 00:22:03.427
He told me, 'I will not let America become a goat nation, for your founding fathers made a covenant with me.'He took me to Plymouth Rock and showed me the pilgrims making a covenant and taking communion.

00:22:03.428 --> 00:22:54.127
He said those prayers still echo in his ears. I saw George Washington crying out on the battlefield, and God gave him strength and victory.

00:22:54.128 --> 00:23:04.898
The Lord said those men died for freedom, and he will not let their blood go.

00:23:04.899 --> 00:23:38.783
He said what we are going through now is not judgment, but correction.

00:23:38.784 --> 00:23:59.278
'True judgment is separation from me for eternity. This is just correction.

00:23:59.279 --> 00:24:25.153
You will be a sheep nation.'He said things are coming to this area and we must draw close to him to hear what's coming.

00:24:25.154 --> 00:24:42.078
There's a shaking coming, but it's a father's love. A great revival is coming, and no man will get the glory.

00:24:42.079 --> 00:25:27.918
I saw glory domes where people were healed by the power of God. People were coming from everywhere to be part of it.

00:25:27.919 --> 00:25:37.950
There was revival happening everywhere, but especially in the center of America.

00:25:37.951 --> 00:25:58.294
Lives were being changed throughout the world—Europe, Africa, everywhere. I want to thank you all for listening.

00:25:58.295 --> 00:26:11.066
I pray, Father, in the name of Jesus, that you anoint these people to do something great.

00:26:11.067 --> 00:26:35.254
Pour out your Spirit. We are the head and not the tail. I take authority over sickness and disease right now. Satan, leave them alone.

00:26:35.255 --> 00:26:48.121
I call them healed and whole by the power of the blood of Jesus, from the top of their heads to the soles of their feet.

00:26:48.122 --> 00:26:58.861
Thank you for the blood and for forgiving our sins. I give you praise and glory for what you're about to do.

00:26:58.862 --> 00:27:21.039
In Jesus'name, have a blessed day, and I appreciate you listening. Bye-bye.

